Java Mini Projects

This repository contains simple Java projects for practice:

💱 Currency Converter A console-based Java program to convert currency between Rupee, Dollar, Pound, Euro, Yen, and Ringgit.

🎯 Number Guessing Game Guess a number between 1-100 within limited attempts. Fun CLI game!

📊 Student Grade Calculator Takes marks for 5 subjects and calculates percentage, grade, and result.
